OL,5, A father-of-two said a headset that    
OL,6, stimulated his brain using electronic  
OL,7, pulses had been a "key part" of his    
OL,8, recovery from depression.              
OL,10,FAshley Riley, from Northamptonshire,   
OL,11,Ftook part in an NHS trial that used the
OL,12,Fdevice to treat the disorder.          
OL,14,FHe signed up after medication alone    
OL,15,Ffailed and said he was now "able to be 
OL,16,Fa full-time dad again".                
OL,18,FProf Alex O'Neill-Kerr, a consultant   
OL,19,Fpsychiatrist, said it may not work for 
OL,20,Fall, but he had seen positive results. 
